snippet.title: 【4K】Bright Memory Infinite / Xbox Series X ( FULL GAMEPLAY )
snippet.description:
Many thanks to all those who purchased Bright Memory during Early Access,
this gave me more confidence to develop Bright Memory: infinite.

I expect to port the Xbox Series X after the PC version is released,this video is a full version with an Easter egg scene, I hope you enjoy it.

Currently bright memory: infinite 80% comes from my own development,
The remaining 20% for UNREAL STORE/QUIXEL/SPEEDTREE/Turbosquid, and help make outsourcing companies.
